Value Required zone (\S+)
Value active (active)
Value target (\S+)
Value icmp_block_inversion (\S+)
Value interfaces (.*)
Value sources (.*)
Value services (.*)
Value ports (.*)
Value protocols (.*)
Value masquerade (\S+)
Value forward_ports (.*)
Value source_ports (.*)
Value icmp_blocks (.*)
Value rich_rule (.+)

Start
  ^${zone}( \(${active}\))?
  ^  target: ${target} -> Record
  ^  icmp-block-inversion: ${icmp_block_inversion} -> Record
  ^  interfaces: ${interfaces} -> Record
  ^  sources: ${sources} -> Record
  ^  services: ${services} -> Record
